    <item>
      <title>特别国会会议让上田有机会引导利率市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/special-diet-session-to-give-ueda-chance-to-steer-market-on-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在市场对日本央行近期加息的押注不断增加的情况下，特别国会会议的开始可能为日本央行行长上田和夫提供一个机会来引导与利率政策相关的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/special-diet-session-to-give-ueda-chance-to-steer-market-on-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 01:54:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国准备对中国芯片实施限制措施 但未达到早先的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/us-readies-china-chip-curbs-that-stop-short-of-earlier-proposals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，拜登政府正在考虑对向中国出售半导体设备和人工智能存储芯片实施进一步限制，此举将加大美国对北京科技野心的打击力度，但不会采取此前考虑过的一些更为严格的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/us-readies-china-chip-curbs-that-stop-short-of-earlier-proposals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 01:43:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚对达尔文港业主陷入困境的报道表示担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/australia-concerned-by-reports-port-of-darwin-s-owner-in-trouble</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚政府将于周四与北领地政府举行会谈，讨论对中国岚桥集团财务状况的担忧。岚桥集团拥有具有重要战略意义的达尔文港 99 年的租约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/australia-concerned-by-reports-port-of-darwin-s-owner-in-trouble</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 01:31:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选加剧贸易风险 韩国央行意外降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/bok-surprises-with-rate-cut-as-trump-s-win-boosts-trade-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行周四在发布较为悲观的增长预测后连续下调利率，令投资者感到意外，此举导致债券收益率下降、股市上涨并重创韩元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/bok-surprises-with-rate-cut-as-trump-s-win-boosts-trade-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:51:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国严厉打击剥削移民工人的企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/uk-launches-crackdown-on-firms-exploiting-migrant-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府宣布严厉打击剥削移民工人的不法雇主，禁止违法者再雇用任何海外员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/uk-launches-crackdown-on-firms-exploiting-migrant-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技公司要求里夫斯简化获取资本的渠道以推动增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/tech-firms-tell-reeves-to-ease-access-to-capital-in-growth-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 希望促进股票市场上市并增强英国的商业竞争力，英国科技公司已要求政府采取进一步行动，改善企业获得资本的渠道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/tech-firms-tell-reeves-to-ease-access-to-capital-in-growth-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称乌克兰需要更多军队而非武器才能赢得战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/us-says-ukraine-needs-more-troops-not-only-weapons-to-win-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫表示，乌克兰必须招募更多士兵来对抗俄罗斯，包括降低征兵年龄，因为该国最迫切的需求是缺乏人力而不是武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/us-says-ukraine-needs-more-troops-not-only-weapons-to-win-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 18:19:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普挑选目标，卢特尼克家收到炸弹威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/trump-transition-says-cabinet-picks-targeted-with-bomb-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[康托·菲茨杰拉德唱片公司的霍华德·卢特尼克是唐纳德·特朗普提名的商务部长人选，他是这位候任总统的政治候选人中受到炸弹威胁和恶意电话攻击最多的人之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/trump-transition-says-cabinet-picks-targeted-with-bomb-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 16:53:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国为何清洗部分高级军事领导人？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/china-military-purge-what-we-know-about-corruption-allegations-xi-s-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平已投入数十亿美元，以实现到 2027 年将军队改造成一支现代化军队的目标。美国情报部门认为，广泛的腐败现象正在破坏习近平的宏伟目标，中国政府还对解放军高层进行了大规模清洗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/china-military-purge-what-we-know-about-corruption-allegations-xi-s-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 09:27:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
